## Available semantic tokens (complete reference)

All tokens below are defined in `src/styles/design-system-tokens/design-system-tokens.css` (semantic `:root` block). Use **only** these in component styles.

### Colors

**Background** (`--color-background-*`):
`brand`, `default`, `weaker`, `weakest`, `stronger`, `strong`, `strongest`

**Border** (`--color-border-*`):
`brand`, `default`, `strong`, `weaker`, `weak`, `inverted`, `brand-weak`,
`system-error`, `system-success`, `system-warning`, `system-info`,
`interactivity-default`, `interactivity-hover`, `interactivity-pressed`, `interactivity-disabled`

**Icons** (`--color-icons-*`):
`brand`, `default`, `weak`, `strongest`, `inverted`, `disabled`, `brand-weaker`,
`system-error`, `system-success`, `system-warning`, `system-info`,
`interactivity-default`, `interactivity-hover`, `interactivity-pressed`, `interactivity-disabled`

**Text** (`--color-text-*`):
`default`, `inverted`, `brand`, `secondary`, `disabled`,
`system-error`, `system-success`, `system-warning`, `system-info`,
`interactivity-default`, `interactivity-hover`, `interactivity-pressed`, `interactivity-disabled`

**Fill** (`--color-fill-*`):

- Common: `common-default`, `common-weaker`, `common-weak`, `common-strong`, `common-stronger`, `common-strongest`, `common-brand`, `common-brand-weak`
- Gradients: `gradients-highlight-stop-1`, `gradients-highlight-stop-2`
- Illustrations: `illustrations-brand-weak-4` through `illustrations-brand-weak-1`, `illustrations-brand`, `illustrations-brand-strong-1` through `illustrations-brand-strong-3`
- System: `system-error-weak`, `system-error-strong`, `system-success-weak`, `system-success-strong`, `system-warning-weak`, `system-warning-strong`, `system-info-weak`, `system-info-strong`
- Interactivity: `interactivity-default`, `interactivity-hover`, `interactivity-pressed`, `interactivity-disabled`

### Typography

**Font family:** `--font-family-heading`, `--font-family-body`, `--font-family-small-details`

**Font weight:** `--font-weight-strong` (500), `--font-weight-default` (400)

**Font size** (`--font-size-*`):
`titles-xxl` (48px), `titles-xl` (32px), `titles-l` (24px), `titles-m` (20px), `titles-s` (16px), `titles-xs` (12px),
`body-m-default` (16px), `body-s` (14px),
`small-details-xs-captions` (12px), `small-details-xxs` (10px)

**Line height** (`--line-height-*`):
`titles-xxl` (56px), `titles-xl` (40px), `titles-l` (32px), `titles-m` (28px), `titles-s` (24px), `titles-xs` (20px),
`body-m-default` (24px), `body-s` (20px),
`small-details-xs-captions` (16px), `small-details-xxs` (16px)

### Spacing

| Token                                              | Resolved value                         |
| -------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| `--spacing-xxs-exception`                          | 4px                                    |
| `--spacing-xs`                                     | 8px                                    |
| `--spacing-s-exception`                            | 12px                                   |
| `--spacing-m`                                      | 16px                                   |
| `--spacing-l`                                      | 24px                                   |
| `--spacing-xl`                                     | 32px                                   |
| `--spacing-xxl`                                    | 40px                                   |
| `--spacing-xxxl`                                   | 48px                                   |
| `--spacing-larger-1` through `--spacing-larger-26` | 56px through 256px (increments of 8px) |

### Corner radius

| Token                 | Resolved value |
| --------------------- | -------------- |
| `--corner-radius-xs`  | 4px            |
| `--corner-radius-s`   | 8px            |
| `--corner-radius-m`   | 12px           |
| `--corner-radius-l`   | 16px           |
| `--corner-radius-xl`  | 24px           |
| `--corner-radius-xxl` | 32px           |

### Icon sizes

| Token            | Resolved value |
| ---------------- | -------------- |
| `--icon-size-xs` | 16px           |
| `--icon-size-s`  | 20px           |
| `--icon-size-m`  | 24px           |
| `--icon-size-l`  | 32px           |
| `--icon-size-xl` | 48px           |

