When unsure about a token name or mapping, consult these files:

| File                                                        | Purpose                                                       |
| ----------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `src/styles/design-system-tokens/design-system-tokens.css`  | Generated CSS with both primitive and semantic `:root` blocks |
